    • Slot

      public Slot(String slotId, String gymId, LocalTime startTime, LocalTime endTime, int capacity, int availableSeats)
      Instantiates a new slot with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      slotId - the unique identifier for the slot
      gymId - the identifier of the gym this slot belongs to
      startTime - the start time of the slot
      endTime - the end time of the slot
      capacity - the maximum capacity of the slot
      availableSeats - the number of available seats in the slot
